MaildirStore gu-local
Path ~/.mail/gu/
Inbox ~/.mail/gu/inbox

Channel gu-inbox
Master :gu-remote:
Slave :gu-local:
Patterns "INBOX"
Create Slave
Remove Slave
SyncState *

Channel gu-sent
Master :gu-remote:"Sent Items"
Slave :gu-local:sent
Create Slave
Remove Slave
SyncState *

Channel gu-trash
Master :gu-remote:"Deleted Items"
Slave :gu-local:trash
Create Slave
Remove Slave
SyncState *

Group gu
Channel gu-inbox
Channel gu-sent
Channel gu-trash